        -:  266:/**
        -:  267:  * \brief Sets a linearly spaced vector.
        -:  268:  *
        -:  269:  * The function generates 'size' equally spaced values in the closed interval [low,high].
        -:  270:  * When size is set to 1, a vector of length 1 containing 'high' is returned.
        -:  271:  *
        -:  272:  * \only_for_vectors
        -:  273:  *
